1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
The seventh day after Cui Wei's death — new faces appeared outside the cold palace.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
My lady, plain-clothes men are lurking out there — too steady to be eunuchs. Trained fighters.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:18,000
How many?

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Three to five, in shifts. Two by day, three by night — they only watch from afar.

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:28,000
The Emperor's men.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
The Emperor? Why would His Majesty watch you?

7
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Because — he fears me.

8
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:44,000
A deposed concubine who can suddenly kill demons. If you were Emperor, wouldn't you fear her?

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:51,000
He won't strike — he needs me more than he fears me. He can't deal with the demon kings at the border.

10
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:58,000
He fears me, but he needs me more. So he sends watchers — not killers.

11
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:03,000
My lady — what should we do?

12
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Nothing.

13
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:14,000
We do nothing. Train. Eat. As long as I don't reach for the throne, he won't move.

14
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Xiao He — find out when I might be granted an audience with His Majesty.

15
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:23,000
You wish to see the Emperor, my lady?

16
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:27,000
Yes. I have a deal to offer.

17
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:34,000
I am done surviving in the cold palace. The demon kings at the border are my offering.

18
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:40,000
And the Emperor — is my pawn.

19
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:46,000
Wait and see. Soon — this palace will know who its true master is.

20
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:52,000
The hunter of the cold palace has turned her gaze — toward the throne.
